		{"id":"anim-test-kling","type":"file","file":"IM8/00 Assets/Statics/energy-textured/backgrounds/anim-tests/coral-botanical-kling/output.mp4","x":12320,"y":4700,"width":279,"height":498},
		{"id":"anim-plan-tier3","type":"text","text":"## Tier 3 — Subtle Ken Burns + Ambient\nOne motion axis. Camera movement + light shifts only.\n\n**coral-mushroom**: lateral pan across gills\n**deep-coral**: caustic light ripple across surface\n**coral-botanical**: rack focus front → back branches\n**clear-bubble**: slow rotation, refraction shifts\n**saffron-threads**: slow rotation of thread bundle\n**chanterelle**: dolly forward into gill folds\n**red-algae**: filaments shift in current\n**ashwagandha-root**: rotation, light catches vascular channels\n**morel-surface**: push into honeycomb pits\n**enoki-cluster**: subtle tremor from air\n**turmeric-cross**: rotation, golden light shift\n**golden-oyster**: lateral pan across yellow gills\n**cordyceps**: push into fibrous interior\n**golden-kelp**: light moves through translucent tissue\n**indigo-milkcap**: lateral pan across blue gills\n**coral-branch**: gentle sway, gradient shifts","x":12320,"y":4110,"width":620,"height":460,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"anim-plan-tier2","type":"text","text":"## Tier 2 — Subject IS the Animation\nNatural behavior = the motion. No zoom needed.\n\n**cell-dividing**: one cell pinches → stretches → separates into two (3-4s)\n**bubble-cluster**: bubbles rising at different speeds, subtle wobble\n**plankton**: drifting/rotating in current, appendages moving\n**thin-film**: iridescent bands slowly flowing across membrane\n**sea-anemone**: tentacles swaying in current, 2-sec pulse cycle\n**soft-coral-polyps**: expanding/contracting — breathing, 3-sec cycle\n**lions-mane**: tendrils cascading with underwater sway","x":12320,"y":3810,"width":620,"height":280,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"anim-plan-tier1","type":"text","text":"## Tier 1 — Microscopic Zoom-Into\nStart human-scale → push into microscopic world → settle\n\n**plant-cells**: leaf blade → cell walls + chloroplasts → organelle drift\n**leaf-stomata**: leaf surface → pore grid → pores pulse open/closed\n**diatoms**: ocean sediment → glass-shell algae → slow rotation\n**mitochondria**: muscle tissue → cell interior → cristae pulse\n**b12-crystals**: pink powder → polarized facets → slow rotation\n**collagen-fibers**: skin surface → blue fiber bundles → stretch/relax\n**nerve-tissue**: brain cortex → neural network → synaptic pulses along axons\n**mycelium-network**: forest floor mushroom → root threads → slow growth","x":12320,"y":3450,"width":620,"height":340,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"anim-plan-principles","type":"text","text":"## Principles\n- **Restraint over spectacle** — supports end card content, never competes\n- **Real physics only** — no bounce, no elastic snap, no particle bursts\n- **2-4 sec motion, then hold** — establish texture, settle, text appears\n- **One axis of motion** — pan OR push OR rotate, never combine\n- **Light shifts > object movement** — move the light, not the subject\n- **Organic deceleration** — things slow from friction, not bezier curves","x":12320,"y":3210,"width":620,"height":220,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"anim-test-label","type":"text","text":"# BG Animation Tests — coral-botanical","x":12320,"y":4610,"width":620,"height":40,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"anim-test-kling-label","type":"text","text":"Kling v3 Pro (5s, $0.56)","x":12320,"y":4660,"width":280,"height":30,"color":"1"},
